<h2>About This App</h2>
<p>This is a very simple Blazor application to manage your tasks.</p>

<h2>Features</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Create new tasks</li>
    <li>Mark tasks as completed</li>
    <li>Delete tasks by double clicking them</li>
    <li>View the percentage of tasks completed</li>
    <li>Persist tasks using local storage</li>
</ul>
